This program simulates a public transportation that consists of buses, bus stops and passengers arriving at stops and boarding buses.

The program contains java source files and a example config file for the simulation.

Config file comes in this format:
    
[number of stops]
[number of buses]
[drive time between stops]
[boarding time]
[simulation time limit]
[passenger spawning rate]

feel free to run the following command to run the simulation.

chmod 755 runSim
./runSim
